                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><h4>Sex: </h4><p class="indent"><span class="tei-persName">Job</span> was male. <a href="/10510-56" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
