                                </span> <a href="/10510-57" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Relationships</h3><p class="indent">Job was a monastic authority over Anonymous 3669. <a href="/10510-59" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
